{"tid":1031208,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)魔女搵老襯 狂/人神魔戰","createTime":"2019-02-21T13:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T17:54:10.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a73a802ddab9ffe0570834190b3ee832b0475d6","tid":1031208,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD5HrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=e787a61b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD5HrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=71b8eb82\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD5HrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=1c83f01f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4f/Bedazzled%282000%29-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4f%2FBedazzled%25282000%2529-poster.jpg&h=4243dba3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/80/Clashofthetitansremakeposter1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F80%2FClashofthetitansremakeposter1.jpg&h=4e03b429&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fe/Wrath_of_the_Titans.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffe%2FWrath_of_the_Titans.jpg&h=4504e1d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.艾略特&middot;里察是一間電腦公司的客戶服務員，但他在公司裏被同事排斥。4年來，他一直暗戀著公司另一部門的女職員──愛麗森，可是，他始終沒有膽去跟她說話。<br />\n有一次，艾略特到酒吧，他碰到因各種原因婉拒與他去酒吧的同事們，不久，他看見愛麗森也來到這裏，在同事們的壓力下，他被迫走過去跟愛麗森談話，不過他最後還是失敗。<br />\n這時，艾略特說：「為了她，我願意付出一切。」突然間，一個非常性感的女人出現，並揚手叫他過來，跟艾略特說她是魔鬼，可以實現他的願望，但代價是要將他的靈魂作為交換條件<br />\n<br />\n2.權力鬥爭促使人民與統治者，及統治者與神之間的對立；但眾神之間的戰爭卻會摧毀整個世界。在人間成長的珀爾修斯（山姆&middot;沃辛頓飾）要從復仇心重的冥王黑帝斯（雷夫&middot;范恩斯飾）手中拯救自己的家人。珀爾修斯憑著無懼勇氣，自薦向冥王宣戰以換取天帝宙斯（連恩&middot;尼遜飾）的神力並解放人間地獄。帕修斯於是帶領著士兵朝著詭異的世界展開冒險之旅。他要戰勝美杜莎和海怪，唯一的方法是接受自己身為神祇的身份，並創造屬於自己的命運<br />\n<br />\n3.擊敗海怪多年後，半人神柏修斯拒絕了宙斯邀請他前往神界治理天下的請求，而是選擇留在凡間當漁夫，並與過世妻子伊俄所生的10歲兒子西里斯過著平凡生活。一天晚上，宙斯下凡探訪柏修斯。因人民不再祈禱，眾神的力量逐漸消失殆盡，且囚禁克羅諾斯地下闇牢將會崩毀，所以宙斯需要同柏修斯合作，以對抗即將到來的威脅。不過，柏修斯因顧慮家人的安全而拒絕參與。隨後，宙斯與其子戰神阿瑞斯及海神波塞頓來到闇牢會見冥王黑帝斯，並向黑帝斯表示要原諒過去的恩怨，聯合重築闇牢。但黑帝斯卻召喚魔獸攻擊宙斯，阿瑞斯趁機窩裡反，襲擊波塞頓並背叛宙斯，奪走了閃電火。黑帝斯與阿瑞斯早就在預謀奪取宙斯的神力來喚醒天神們的父親克羅諾斯，並以此換取永垂不朽<br />\n<br />\n9 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD5HrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=0256eb17\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD5HrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=b46f91aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1caf376351069a007cd4a220a2f71a8e194fb943","tid":1031208,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87bffb16adb339023550ff25e251ac1a4e63eab","tid":1031208,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bea945ba0568bd15df4d1cf58a6272f3f7e174","tid":1031208,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ea0e85052843dad73b8f0896b96dd090f489ab","tid":1031208,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93209814092011b962c8503eeb69b4f89a0abdd1","tid":1031208,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}